timeline.message:
Add pluginExecutionFilter for maven-plugin-plugin

I set up a new Eclipse 2019.12 workspace and I was complaining about
this plugin config in fhir-tools.  After adding the
pluginExecutionFilter that error is gone.

Signed-off-by: Lee Surprenant <lmsurpre@us.ibm.com>
